QuestData.Title: Carrier Has Arrived
QuestData.Description: We're going to get some payback on that little stinker.$B$BPut the baby goren into one of those carriers and then make a special delivery to Thaelin.
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver the Baby Goren Carrier to Thaelin Darkanvil at Telaari Station.
QuestData.RewardText: Wait a minute, $n... let's be reasonable. I can hear what's in that carrier.$B$BIt was just a harmless prank.$B$BDon't do it, please!$B$BStop!$B$BDon't open that carrier!
